      <sparkle:version>24</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.1.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>New high-contrast app icon: burnt-orange bands on the gold planet body, clearly distinct on every theme.</li><li>Recent tab now respects the team scope filter for projects and initiatives, not just issues.</li><li>Cleaner copy-link affordance: hover any row in Mine, Recent, Search, or Faves to reveal a copy icon in its own column instead of overlaying the identifier.</li><li>Pulse stacked bars use a distinct categorical palette (blue / orange / emerald) tuned for light and dark backgrounds.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
